longDescription.stringValue: Make your kitchen shine with the Solt Freestanding Dishwasher in sleek black. The adjustable upper rack allows you to fit tall items with ease while the 3/6/9 hour delay start gives you flexibility. With an energy rating of 3 stars, this dishwasher aims to save you money on bills without compromising on performance. The 10.7 litre per minute water usage and Eco wash program help conserve water for more eco-friendly dishwashing. The child lock provides extra safety and peace of mind. Thanks to the intuitive electronic controls, operating this dishwasher is simple. It produces just 52 decibels of noise so you can run a cycle without disturbances. The stainless steel interior resists stains and rust to keep your dishwasher looking pristine wash after wash. With a width of 598mm, height of 895mm and depth of 600mm, this dishwasher is designed to fit most kitchen spaces. It sits on adjustable feet for leveling on uneven floors. Rely on this dishwasher to handle tough loads for years to come and enjoy the 2 year manufacturer's warranty for added assurance. The manufacturer's part number for this product is GGSDW6012B. Check out this Solt dishwasher if you want a quality appliance with modern styling and eco-friendly performance.
